ke)表示。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;在一些备受瞩目的企业破产导致人们对贷款质量和软件公司风险敞口日益担忧之后&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;，1.8万亿美元的私人信贷市场&lt;/strong&gt;正在见证&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/claD9-hve0bBiD7VuIE9ml6leM3FPVMu9ouZ9FHfcABpGAwezafoiobRnz-t-qrPrDfvMEARTY3h7ccVl_cPGh30CnDV1NcUqjNnDUC-vTQhUwizs_o7KY14zBxKsZXO9adecKq-VT5nAX8p4oopb59Nd9V_IFIRClWiNQNKJs_dpLlnljJlt56TpGJRFzWc58jNX5Dm67D2vrWnB0spN3n2b_ftT9efppULzECtyVc_xAY5u8klZW9OGxIMCzaCu9vu1mKsuEUWT4WHI-nlr6Tnh03y4et7j3w8rHkfoh2zXBWqHn_QCrIH4Zdt7DmJKqAJBY5dSffHoYyvLNYvR0aHClRzSWpLkNNAJZS4PF8DAA-0naNPDhQP4bY/1gabwVY3s8md-V8u70iBBNMUgcPRiMZw/18" target="_blank"&gt;投资者的大批撤离&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;据称，摩根大通&lt;/strong&gt;在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RhWDcHrS0V-pInwOO-yvuGVvR_51HvoQBhxvXH3gSGpI-uVk_HpePauYRvKw68nUf8qOukVVCZL5Y7RiNCKVrxVdaQ-aSeE5ql-utqjDkk8fRr_gCR8Gu_tiH0F9lwKtkX7hs7Z6hS6p1mDgKU1ARJhw1VbCoGiHSJrhcmdDw8jc1uCnI0J0KuSsbhbeuIQMSo_UuZktYeWAh6T-uEp2F1W898NDrSbljjNpz6ep9s_rVLtgMIBvqesqYjnYrmku7SqZ5TYFO9rSCf5J3LUdrZ0CR-EcZfvtpKtn0I7C0tPUBL56M7P_IZGAv1HVIP6XXZNlW5-9EmSCTUWRhoYCQn9R_O5rh-8S9aS9Lyb52RGo1KW2wzpdYD6sFx0/b_GKd75_DM_fYNyPDB59nZoEKIxWlOTS/18" target="_blank"&gt;降低其投资组合中某些贷款的价值&lt;/a&gt;后，将限制向私人信贷基金提供部分贷款。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;而且情况可能会变得更糟。&lt;/strong&gt;太平洋投资管理公司警告说，该领域&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dD48Y6JnwAbbzuaapLz43yTzWUcH5M3POBabdo14U0EZEiwJz9L8sn0HNh1SPI85_02KcoNZnN0U0ZGDwS4olcU30G4sMnHPI_Y0NreOr-Y_2r_EDnA0qlICkmfnOR3mAZMNfqAJ2ERhWxCa9nzOczEINnQgdHwv_4GjDBSs5yalpo5gufPwipX2B5YFjwQpooZwiUez5KZnCFznlpm-Hezot556HJyJV-llLz354_cLj0-gv8KNo0Hqnkbw_JroryvLTIpQRB9USRdm1Miu_Dyw_Wt6QngdQ9-sWWBWav6hrRIFWEY4Wo2TlBzgLhZ1KZ30U5Z4aIT4cONB-Pn6VCq-m