px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;封闭式基金 Pershing Square USA 的首次公开募股还将让投资者获得他的另类资产管理公司 Pershing Square 的股份。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TymrRpcNT3jM5wZnLqVoG2EcWD8w6O5MhvB2Z-7k8d5lXgQJxTUiKhBiVTiiat8ytjfsb83YShUwEt3X1ltUlR9APJ_3jJ0yFqhvYfSjC527whLCVhmmU9C648aS-cuM8EDZMaM-W_q5f7DHU-UF4rJYUAljianvylQhNhMRG2ccOXoPqgeph30ievXflq2AV7Dgrv0pkJZmtf_Tu8gcLKRMSq4AOhHzdq_rDslqOrvxxMGUqlwEGey9nbLkP2gEdfkx5cYQdctNBTgL4pTWXDBqrCs2knec_wP7mOHXPW20PcdTh4eo8XXdw5XLNUCb7WxVmjNiBOz4687lARtT_JHCt2UVvVyDEKTQka-gN9bKyXI/ALWJ33Ashcza_xM3V1D4e9d9ceJqy1MP/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;文件显示&lt;/a&gt;，买方每购买 100 股封闭式基金 IPO，投资者将获得管理公司 20 股。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;阿克曼希望在合并交易中为 Pershing Square USA 筹集 50 亿至 100 亿美元的资金，以每股 50 美元购买封闭式基金股票的投资者将获得管理公司的股票，无需额外费用。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/wUHVGKSC083YdIn6wvirBTEkzlSBNzJjBUFbu37XFW-QMc_Sje45yioqifS7FoH--zWO1aPIt1y9VxD1rY9DgPSDBqtuf3bMleiv5cSBTMbsEa2nIRUJv2Pa5OY75l50Pvf7uNWPbi_As7GZqsK9GoWJH1IeBvQ-jVsK1ybPl2OFzshk2DaMKRfTWDvEPI9O2XfkKOYgvxMAx9MgC5yUb47Mn7d3DAwNPDZJfDHGxtmEo-YizBUKzbwn2Lf7s50L4fJ6Wh6l4tnHKmmxcu8svIecOzYcGx5-y_AA29rXu7SKHYV1F122ZPfMcMl9YqVfPX6jpggo4SQ8mJQRfZwDLS5iE7RtVKOPFnAY-bUIvrmHD7ZTd_1b7Q/yWlGnOWIRUQlQbPVeRwflInIQ6FcJog5/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itP2NJ7x4fn0/v0/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Bill Ackman, chief executive officer of Pershing Square Capital Management LP, speaks during an interview for an episode of &amp;quot;The David Rubenstein Show: Peer-to-Peer Conversations&amp;quot; in New York, US, on Tuesday, Nov. 28, 2023. Ackman in October said he covered his short bet on US Treasuries, noting &amp;quot;there is too much risk in the world to remain short bonds at current long-term rates.&amp;quot; Photographer: Jeenah Moon/Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="潘兴广场资本管理公司首席执行官比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 于 2023 年 11 月 28 日星期二在美国纽约接受“大卫·鲁宾斯坦秀：点对点对话”一集采访时发表讲话。阿克曼 10 月份表示，他回补了美国国债的空头押注，并指出“按照目前的长期利率，世界上存在太多风险，无法继续做空债券。”摄影师：Jeenah Moon/彭博社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itP2NJ7x4fn0/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;彭博社观点&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;比尔·阿克曼回来了，他再次想要你的钱&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在伊朗战争引发油价飙升并引发通胀担忧后，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;债券交易员已转向押注&lt;/strong&gt;美国国债损失，大举&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/JJDw7-deBBCUISJxiBxBe5IGW6sPuDHW5TpaHGPNIzRWR_KFP2zCNGe-CvBVl8TgYUlrslLa4Qb_RLYTEs1EjsNrBiOyAAA-R3xQOzTMxlHS92-xfM2rRWTx0VWNVNemqChVagcpT4-eMfRh8MRxLXGUmmLAlsvHazViTmkJ0z6iJEEhkKB80omXrju6SkrQsWmhp_eOAxSbWz0nGyH5w1nj5EROMrhR7Hv0QJHNnUlsS7HST3tkj_drKj1rItH8eP-aRu0ioXHdvt4j0sSd6NG-bkYQ40Gh4QfTUYDiczMl0Yfl7cHcM2Ww8s5E09rBGUTGgCQyAHAjeAxA0dTj2JXVnF6xldbpa6pND3tpE04j1wrZS_BlNdxgHFrr1AHvQeIJtf_KxiWpRSYKRQLpFJQYMMGi_oeNGXe2LcQ1h9M4FO8JAbUKB3xWCwrpFzuphj0J6yJ-lkOATwwAIe-4ShnDuBetUehTa44NjhkD8Ghq97ynEZdiws7t28PFDI3x9JAc8kQ/QA_ITOw5zXyCBmt5eCHY0MUP8FoUK-O-/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着战争的爆发，交易员转而做空美国国债"&gt;抛售看涨期货头寸&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;