iCzW5HoKvXBaEafY9468mDxjcCZBuKj9eNKAdAoz28CV1WDN_KwUj9mukgoIdsLfBGnQKqvhh1xaOXIZYjcvbwmHB4T6e_ZkkP3IjLHTib2ufKtN5lO8GAVVqYUNdKZm9uFd67klr26iyrr6hYA2STLp7fAAQeg27bscSbaF0Fax7Ncs5Tp_G31pjUfpMXXBrV3Q0/4av-n7Pm5f1AvdFuV08q_NfOLRqkLePI/18" target="_blank"&gt;非法任命三名律师&lt;/a&gt;在阿丽娜·哈巴辞去新泽西州最高联邦检察官职务后接替她。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普实施移民镇压&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一年&lt;/strong&gt;后，我们几乎没有看到任何证据表明更严格的边境政策正在改善美国出生的工人的就业前景。移民紧缩&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Hp2Oux5Ov1_SRGvU5ISXgxiyuXD3fdlhq_72AASnPiCdgFZNbCF_2FFEUPdOOZveeHfsNOHBdl0LEaZiDn8bYEXCfA_oJlgeSpX6C8JJ1UvXs3pvgjxELj9jafcSc6HxyewR9MDg_pugKB0sqynY4bPOqtpdmltZsn5ujzoOHpYzbcfiBuaq-ezfS36lhblPws4l4MUSygAbQ3lctblQfUQ-obmEyJpn8rb4ynMbT0M5IOqrSsg5oWPkQOGFVoN8RvL3rN0b3CR999GOMRwy1vDRZJOrI4eH2UarLCPHiHqIh_OO15cj1NSe36E8gBvoEMEk_K3-bj4dao6ciqDH8HtkISa3jTIqHsUw6asXhuU7-_3L0xGIn_hOKU4/6x600zwde3VEvC6ZZGgC6mRFoYN2GQI3/18" target="_blank" title="工作机会"&gt;与本土出生的失业率上升&lt;/a&gt;同时发生，尽管一些企业表示填补职位空缺变得越来越困难。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/c3vcvI4vuSyWFojv5NLf6FsZkfZ_yYPEJVqtKaJB3uIO6wsFHY_Uapb0pAQpjn1YeHUtAhcHN1yuc8hyu9Ho9BdlVkg8wkMUdUveibfiU_x4q_qczf0lngug1HWm1EYlhvDdwIDDOjAzzqKFp8xARtMbgndW-meoYMq7ig2GqEMxEJOto-2tnrrwCWuhvUd-0Ml67aXyGmkUMm1DsYYg6cCfcI8RWfrFGBBgaHi3hJ2Yrr_ej0do57H7I-FazErU2Ohy7wRXTtcx8RNsHucs6BEQoj7DI5uU-nzqApz8nI6COr9_QEMg-up_mlDh26s4dYtrncm_6jwxRXOCYU0XgwHPTW6K_J_LW7iQisMqwJnswV4dl_DmL2hiTUQ/jbSCT16RtYHFMkgxIcWVZw714CS8ZKnm/18" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4tdJO9jUgSc/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4tdJO9jU